      "text": [
        " : \"أَوَّلُ قَطْرَةٍ مِنْ دَمِ اَلشَّهِيدِ كَفَّارَةٌ لِذُنُوبِهِ إِلاَّ اَلدَّيْنَ فَإِنَّ كَفَّارَتَهُ قَضَاؤُهُ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3688 - It is narrated from Aban, from Bashshar, from Abu Ja'far Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) who said: \"The first drop of the martyr's blood is an expiation for his sins-except for debt, for its expiation is its repayment.\""
        ]
      }
